danbikel.parser

Class PrintDisn

  • java.lang.Object
    • danbikel.parser.PrintDisn

  • public class PrintDisn
extends Object
    Provides a single static method, printLogProbDisn, as well as a main(String[]) method, to print a log-probability distribution for a particular event in a particular model of a model collection.

      • printLogProbDisn

        public static void printLogProbDisn(PrintWriter writer,
                    ModelCollection mc,
                    Model model,
                    int level,
                    Event hist,
                    Set futures,
                    Transition tmpTrans)
        Prints the log-probability distribution of the specified event at the specified back-off level of the specified model to the specified writer.
        Parameters:
        writer - the writer to which to print a log-probability distribution
        mc - the model collection containing the specified model
        model - the model from which an event's log-probability distribution is to be printed
        level - the back-off level of the specified event
        hist - the event whose distribution is to be printed
        futures - the set of futures for the specified history
        tmpTrans - a temporary storage object used during the invocation of this method
